Automated Co-registration of EO-1 large offsets

Goal #1
- Get access to usgs landsat-8 surface reflectance NDVI data
- Find best and most recent Landsat-8 scene(s)
- Find best tile to match particular EO-1 scene

You need USGS machine to machine proviledge

http://earthexplorer.usgs.gov/inventory/documentation/json-api

